# API Testing Notes

In-project notes for testing {{PROJECT_DISPLAY_NAME}} APIs. Trigger skill: `/{{PROJECT_NAME}}-api-tester` (defined at `~/.claude/skills/{{PROJECT_NAME}}-api-tester/SKILL.md`).

## Authentication

1. Token is stored per env at `config/tokens/<env>.json` as `{"token": "<bearer>"}`.
2. If `request.sh` errors with `No token file for environment 'X'`, paste a fresh curl from browser DevTools.

